# Form Pattern

## Structure

- Visible labels on every field (placeholder ≠ label)
- Group with sections / grids (`FormSection`, `FormGrid`, `SweetFormField`)
- Primary actions in a footer with clear separation (border-top)
- Destructive secondary actions visually separated

## Validation

- Zod schema at boundary (action or client+server)
- Field-level errors; focus first invalid field when practical
- Disable submit while pending

## Complexity ladder

| Complexity | Approach |
|------------|----------|
| Simple dialog | Controlled state + `useTransition` |
| Auth | `useActionState` + form action |
| Complex multi-field | RHF + Zod |
| Multi-step | Wizard with explicit steps + back/next |

## Mobile

Inputs must not force horizontal overflow; modals must fit viewport (no taller-than-screen traps without scroll).
